{
  "id": 5154752085884928,
  "name": "View Transitions: Inherit more animation properties",
  "summary": "Similar to https://chromestatus.com/feature/5424291457531904, which inherited animation-delay, this feature adds more animation properties to inherit through the view transition pseudo tree based on resolution in https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/11546#issuecomment-3005503138:\r\n* animation-timing-function\r\n* animation-iteration-count\r\n* animation-direction\r\n* animation-play-state",
